{
 "name": "RPlog_Myiari_s_Date",
 "title": "Myiari's Date",
 "summary": "In the entertainment district of New Alderaan, the medic Myiari meets the gunman Brek for a dinner date at a quiet bistro. Over steaks, dumplings, and Corellian ale, the two ease into warm, teasing conversation about their professions, self-defense, holodramas, romance novels, and the awkwardness of unwanted attention. Brek gallantly recalls scaring off a leering patron earlier, and the pair trade stories about pilots, family, and their respective jobs with growing comfort and mutual amusement. As the evening winds down they realize they are running short on time for a show they had planned to catch, capping off a relaxed and genuinely pleasant date.",
